docs/architecture/spec-program-plan.md:111:> - **Contradiction 3** (`docs/specs/v1-core-spec.md` + `docs/specs/v1-surfaces-spec.md`): **Resolved.** `OutboundEvent.surfaceId` is optional; `OutboundEventError` is defined; the targeted-send vs. session-fanout normative rule is documented in both specs.
