docs/specs/v1-surfaces-spec.md:238:   * - 'continue': attempt all surfaces; collect errors; return FanoutResult.
docs/specs/v1-surfaces-spec.md:239:   * - 'abort': throw on first error; remaining surfaces are not attempted.
docs/specs/v1-surfaces-spec.md:245:   * Whether to skip inactive surfaces silently.
